{"tid":1755762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今鋪連黑警同癈老都支持我地光復香港","createTime":"2019-11-25T17:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T18:21:02.000Z","uid":319687,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"988a03c4728be98956a40abac0d9d29396c2ca17","tid":1755762,"uid":319687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"政治唔單止要支持你既人支持<br />\n更加需要<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔支持你既人支持</span></strong>, <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>包括黑警 同 癈老</strong></span></strong><br />\n咁我地先至會<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">完勝</span></span></strong>, 光復到香港<br />\n<br />\n<strong>有餘錢剩既, </strong><br />\n1, 請用任何方法, 聘請, 支援一位前線 / 被補手足, 做文宣又好, 咩都好<br />\n(我而家每月3千蚊請佐位手足幫我每日做2個鐘海外文宣, 可以係呢度請人 --&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=d2ba720f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a>)<br />\n<br />\n2, 堅持所有消費只會係黃店, 不論係食飯, 買野, 搭車, 每一蚊我都係只會比支持香港民主相關的鋪頭/集團, 呢個堅持就係真正既黃色經濟圈, 可以係呢度找到: <a href=\"https://wordsofmouth.net\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwordsofmouth.net&d=yZvzIFdj7oCTZXRWgogUmRYTjY4AGk5vqx1zl%2FZrtgc%3D&h=631d5559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wordsofmouth.net</a><br />\n<strong><br />\n有力既, 唔該</strong><br />\n1, 做文宣, 係twitter又好, 微博又好, 貼連濃牆又好, 總之目的係要令更多原先唔支持我地既人支持我地, 就係咁簡單<br />\n<br />\n2, 參與區內區議員既活動, 幫街坊解決社區的問題也好, 搞活動也好, 探訪又好, 定期播片又好, 做資料搜集又好, 目的係要做好區內的社關工作, 建立口碑, 我地要<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">反醒</span></strong>泛民地方工作之前失民心既地方, 民主香港唔係得把口講, 我地要用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>真正既行動</strong></span></span>去話比d街坊知, 民主香港係會有一個點樣既未來同希望, 同中國共產黨講既on9野有咩唔同, <strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我講多次, 係用行動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n3, 參與抗爭, 和你lunch又好, 和你sing 又好, 和你shop又好, 整聯署又好, 1823搞9鄉黑又好, 隨身帶定口罩隨時on call, 附近有活動立即可以參加, 具備water 既特性<br />\n<br />\n而家先係致係岩岩係區議會攞佐未來4年既入場卷,<br />\n區議員1個人仲要加埋大家每一位先至光復到自己果區<br />\n令更多唔支持我地既人係不久既將來成為我地既手足<br />\n大家要加把勁!!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我好期待黑警掉轉槍頭, 大大聲咁屌中國共產黨<br />\n我好期待癈佬愛國唔愛黨, 大大聲咁屌中國共產黨<br />\n我更加期待光復到香港, 煲底下大家相見</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人, 加油</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"223fd08557874c8dc76b4a4b34553879c76555b2","tid":1755762,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:03:31.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"},{"pid":"463abb81d7ec2891872f70d28e90ef8134bc994b","tid":1755762,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:03:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"034b418b19dad6e354f520fe51e5eae97a9ec0aa","tid":1755762,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:04:45.000Z","msg":"黃店邀請區議員到舖支持！"},{"pid":"a1ee740c1ab658407f9375b0fb19464acbae7278","tid":1755762,"uid":268246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:06:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ced8d86e6c8f823dd2aef4a78c66e765f1605dba","tid":1755762,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:07:38.000Z","msg":"唉雖然理想既社會演變的確係要啲仆街警察變節<br />\n但我真係好想佢地死撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地殺撚左好多人啊"},{"pid":"7670f8f67e1edc1865c38db96e1991ef4fb2b761","tid":1755762,"uid":308095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T18:10:22.0